parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, become stuck in gear, or refuse to shift, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission locks up
the vehicle loses power
the transmission fails to shift into gear
the transmission jumps out of gear
a loud thumping or grinding noise is heard
the vehicle becomes stuck in reverse gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Torque converter failure can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power, difficulty shifting, or complete failure of the transmission.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage
the vehicle hesitates or stutters when shifting
a loud grinding or whining noise is heard
the transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating.
